        <item>
            <title>新 Apple Watch 或加入血压监测，功能推出初期有一定限制</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/19/next-gen-apple-watch-could-offer-limited-blood-pressure-monitoring/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=next-gen-apple-watch-could-offer-limited-blood-pressure-monitoring</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/19/next-gen-apple-watch-could-offer-limited-blood-pressure-monitoring/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[唐美凤]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 02:00:07 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[潮流手表]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple Watch Series 10]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[血压]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1225134</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>根据《彭博》作者 Mark Gurman 在新一期 Power On 专栏的说法，今年推出的 Apple Watch Series 10 将会加入血压监测功能，但在推出时会有一些限制。近年推出的 Apple Watch 配备多种健康感应器，能够监测用户的心率、血氧、体温等数据，亦因此吸引了不少想监测自己健康的消费者，作出佩戴 Apple Watch 的选择。</p><p><span id="more-1225134"></span></p><p>Mark Gurman 爆料指今年秋季推出的 Apple Watch Series 10，新增的血压监测功能会比较简单，只会告知用户其血压有否上升趋势，但就不会显示实际上下压。专栏中指要获得准确的血压读数仍需数年时间，而新功能似乎需要配合新的硬件，因此 Apple Watch Series 9 或之前的型号可能无法透过系统更新提供。</p><p>今年将会是 Apple Watch 产品的第 10 代，专栏指 Apple 会作出重大变革，除了加入血压监测，还会在整体设计著手，例如令表身变得更薄，同时改用占用空间更少的全新表带连接系统。</p><p>资料及图片来源：<a href="https://www.cultofmac.com/835661/next-gen-apple-watch-could-offer-limited-blood-pressure-monitoring/">cultofmac</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/05/hermes-apple-watch/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">全新 Hermès Apple Watch 表带登场，与其他系列共新增 22 款</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/03/microled-apple-watch-ultra-canceled-for-now/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">供应商暗示项目触礁   Apple Watch Ultra 改用 microLED 屏幕无望</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/12/apple-watch-series-9-ultra-2-touch-screen-issue/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Apple Watch Series 9 触控问题，官方展开调查 Ultra 2 亦受影响</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/19/next-gen-apple-watch-could-offer-limited-blood-pressure-monitoring/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/">新 Apple Watch 或加入血压监测，功能推出初期有一定限制</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
