        </item>
        <item>
            <title>【评测】Sony FE 24-50mm F2.8 G 轻巧天涯镜，人像实试 + 微距出色</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/18/sony-fe-24-50mm-f2-8-g-review/dc/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=sony-fe-24-50mm-f2-8-g-review</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/18/sony-fe-24-50mm-f2-8-g-review/dc/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 12:42:24 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[数码相机]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[相机测试]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[24-50mm]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[SONY]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[镜头]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1225016</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>以往 f/2.8 大光圈变焦镜头，例如大三元镜头 f/2.8 16-35mm, 24-70mm, 70-200mm 都是好多摄影爱好者的目标。始终光圈够大，在夜晚拍摄杂讯会少得多，而且能制造迷人散景效果。今次 Sony 提出了一个超强性价比的全新 f/2.8 大光圈选择，就是这次介绍的 Sony FE 24-50mm F2.8 G。它的焦段比较特别，但重点是价格相宜、轻巧设计，同时兼备相当不错的性能。当然这种平靓正的镜头，用上手还是会感到有少许限制，是否容许这些限制，成为你入手这支性价比超强镜头的最后考虑。以下小编就同 unwire 记者 Keiko 一齐到公园试用此镜。分析这镜头的特点与分享使用感受。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225098" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09275-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09275-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09275.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><a title="DSC08904" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/53595588890/in/album-72177720315512572/" data-flickr-embed="true" data-header="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53595588890_7e539abba5_c.jpg" alt="DSC08904" width="800" height="533" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>▲以下所有试相，点击图片后可进入 Flickr 相簿放大阅览</p><p>＞＞＞<a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/albums/72177720315512572/">点击进入 Flickr 相簿可看所有试相</a>＜＜＜</p><h2>光学性能与定位</h2><p>这支镜头属于著重性价比的 Sony G 镜头系列，同 G Master 系列作一个区隔。但单从光圈等规格、性能上，它绝不会比 GM 镜头差得多。就光学性能来说，它在 24-70mm G Master 第一代和 G Master 第二代之间，但就提供体积更小的镜身，重量也只有 440 克。今时今日的用家已追求轻便实用，A7C 系列大卖就是最好证明，而这支镜头也非常适合 A7C 系列机身。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225111" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09242-694x467.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="467" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09242-694x467.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09242.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225100" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09286-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09286-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09286.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225101" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09287-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09287-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09287.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Sony FE 24-50mm F2.8 G 最长焦距只是去到 50mm，但对于好多朋友去旅行、平时街拍，50mm 已经非常够用。要考虑到它的轻细镜身与只是 GM 镜头一半的价格，可说是合理的等价交换。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225102" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09267-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09267-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09267.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225108" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09294-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09294-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09294.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲A7CR 配合附加手柄后，用上此镜刚刚好</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225109" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09295-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09295-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09295.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲A7CR 就算没有加手柄，机身与镜头比例也是很不错</p><p>以相片拍摄的成像清晰度来说，Sony FE 24-50mm F2.8 G 无论在 24mm 至到 50mm 都能拍出令人满意的相片。在全开光圈时的成像锐利度与对比度都非常不错，能够与第一代 G Master 镜头媲美。而在人像拍摄时产生的背景浅景深效果，也紧贴了 GM 镜头的水准。当然需要极致柔滑散景，你还得尝试一下第二代 GM 镜头，但在 G 镜上所得的相片已经很满意。</p><p><a title="DSC08912" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/53595345223/in/album-72177720315512572/" data-flickr-embed="true" data-header="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53595345223_24d816760a_c.jpg" alt="DSC08912" width="800" height="533" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC08945" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/53595457064/in/album-72177720315512572/" data-flickr-embed="true" data-header="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53595457064_0d08c403c0_c.jpg" alt="DSC08945" width="800" height="533" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>▲相片经过颜色后制处理</p><p><a title="DSC08968" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/53595345018/in/album-72177720315512572/" data-flickr-embed="true" data-header="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53595345018_58b4defaea_c.jpg" alt="DSC08968" width="800" height="533" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC09002" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/53594263322/in/album-72177720315512572/" data-flickr-embed="true" data-header="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53594263322_01e36ef7e5_c.jpg" alt="DSC09002" width="800" height="533" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>▲相片经过颜色后制处理</p><h2>为何 24-50mm 已经够用</h2><p>Sony FE 24-50mm F2.8 G 规格上同 24-70mm F2.8 GM 对比，最明显就只有缺乏了 51-70mm 的方面的焦段，但这焦段通常用来实现人物、景物的特写。而事实上在此镜头中，你已经拥有 24mm、28mm、35mm 以及 50mm 这几个常用焦段，有关特写的拍摄，亦可用「人肉」变焦自己走近一点便可（撇除压缩感等因素）。24-50mm 这个焦段已相当够用，绝对是一支适合旅游、日常影相拍 vlog、影食饭的「天涯镜」。</p><p>24mm：私房人像近摄、广阔风景照</p><p>28mm：较繁忙街道的街拍、风景照、人物 + 风景照</p><p>35mm：较阔街道的街拍、风景照、人像相片、人物 + 风景照</p><p>50mm：街拍中突显街中某单一人物或事物、具有迷人景深的人像相片</p><p><a title="DSC08940" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/53595457109/in/album-72177720315512572/" data-flickr-embed="true" data-header="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53595457109_322580a401_c.jpg" alt="DSC08940" width="533" height="800" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>▲约 35mm（人物加景物）</p><p><a title="DSC08996" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/53595588290/in/album-72177720315512572/" data-flickr-embed="true" data-header="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53595588290_52f52873c5_c.jpg" alt="DSC08996" width="800" height="533" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>▲约 40mm（人物加景物）相片经过颜色后制处理</p><p><a title="DSC09005" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/53594263292/in/album-72177720315512572/" data-flickr-embed="true" data-header="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53594263292_feab49032f_c.jpg" alt="DSC09005" width="800" height="533" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>▲50mm（人物）颜色经过后制处理</p><p><a title="DSC08977" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/53594263852/in/album-72177720315512572/" data-flickr-embed="true" data-header="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53594263852_e2fbea42b0_c.jpg" alt="DSC08977" width="533" height="800" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC09202" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/53595344473/in/album-72177720315512572/" data-flickr-embed="true" data-header="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53595344473_bfe378c54f_c.jpg" alt="DSC09202" width="800" height="533" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC09203" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/53595137091/in/album-72177720315512572/" data-flickr-embed="true" data-header="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53595137091_77628eb4b0_c.jpg" alt="DSC09203" width="800" height="533" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/21/sony-fe-24-50mm-f2-8-g/dc/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【现场评测】Sony FE 24-50mm F2.8 G 现埸实试　新焦段+轻巧+画质媲美第一代 G Master</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2>镜身在 50mm 焦段缩到最短，便利人像摄影用家<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></h2><p>一般镜头包括 GM 那款 24-70mm f/2.8 镜头，其外变焦设计是在最广角端如 24mm 收起所有镜片到镜筒，在使用 35mm、50mm 时部份镜片才会从镜筒中突起。今次 Sony FE 24-50mm F2.8 G 却相反在 50mm 焦段时就把所有镜片收起于镜筒内，反倒是在镜头变 wide 时才会把镜筒伸出。这种设计很适合基本用于人像摄影的用家，在使用 50mm 拍摄时镜筒收到最紧致，就算是 35mm 镜筒都只是略为突起。</p><p>50mm 至到 24mm 的镜筒伸出状况：</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225104" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09274-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09274-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09274.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲50mm</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225105" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09273-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09273-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09273.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲35mm</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225106" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09272-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09272-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09272.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲28mm</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225107" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09271-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09271-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09271.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲24mm</p><h2>对焦性能不下于 GM 镜头</h2><p>Sony FE 24-50mm F2.8 G 装备有两个线性自动对焦马达，能够与高速连拍相机如 A9 III 配合使用，达到每秒 120 帧的对焦追踪。即使在今次试用的 A7CR 高像素相机中，仍可保持高速而准确的连续对焦。感觉上镜头对焦速度已同 GM 镜头相当接近。尤其是人像拍摄，捕捉眼睛的准确度、速度都极高，就算被摄者转身，也能快速切换至人物驱体侦测，不会突然迷焦。当人物转身返回正面，对焦可重回被摄者眼睛上，整个过程都是极为顺滑的。</p><p><a title="DSC08927" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/53595588815/in/album-72177720315512572/" data-flickr-embed="true" data-header="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53595588815_4495c33603_c.jpg" alt="DSC08927" width="800" height="533" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>▲只要镜头内有人物，相机＋镜头可高速对焦人物眼睛、脸部、驱体</p><h2>小心畸边控制</h2><p>不过此镜最需要的，就是配合机身内置的镜头补正功能。镜头整体来说在机身修正之下，畸变现象几乎消失。但如果关闭修正功能，在 24mm 焦段出现的桶型畸变会较为明显，即使在 50mm 焦段仍会有一点点畸变现象发生，这会令到人像摄影中被摄者脸部肌肉看上去会更加厚。无论如何，这次小编与 Keiko 合作的人像相片测试中，未有发现明显脸部变肥的情况。</p><p><a title="DSC08924" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/53594263702/in/album-72177720315512572/" data-flickr-embed="true" data-header="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53594263702_de2b39a375_c.jpg" alt="DSC08924" width="800" height="533" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><h2>近摄都无问题</h2><p>在 24mm 焦段时 Sony FE 24-50mm F2.8 G 的最近对焦距离为 0.19 米、在 50mm 焦段时最近对焦距离 0.3 米，最大放大倍率为 0.3x。虽然未有 GM 镜那般强横，但也完全在实用领域。在旅行时用来拍摄食物、小摆设，它都能够应付自如。突显到 Sony FE 24-50mm F2.8 G 是一支全能的天涯镜。</p><p><a title="DSC08987" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/53595456714/in/album-72177720315512572/" data-flickr-embed="true" data-header="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53595456714_75985cc981_c.jpg" alt="DSC08987" width="800" height="533" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>▲相片经过颜色后制处理</p><p>除了线性马达，在其他功能方面 Sony FE 24-50mm F2.8 G 都与 GM 镜头十分类似，例如有齐可无段变换、逐格变换的光圈环、可自订功能的操作按钮、可抵受微雨的密封设计等。镜头配备的花形遮光罩在实际用途之外，也令到整副装备看上去十分专业。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225103" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09260-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09260-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09260.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/21/sony-fe-24-50mm-f2-8-g/dc/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【现场评测】Sony FE 24-50mm F2.8 G 现埸实试　新焦段+轻巧+画质媲美第一代 G Master</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2>总结：高性价比大光圈天涯镜</h2><p>Sony FE 24-50mm F2.8 G 的官方建议零售价是 HK$8,990，是另一支更高阶 GM 镜头 Sony FE 24-70mm F2.8 GM II 价格 HK$17,990 的一半，价格因素可谓不容忽视。在大家都好渴望需要一支大光圈镜头，而 Sony 现在有一支涵盖 24mm 至到 50mm 焦段的镜头面世，不吸引才是假的。此镜头为用户提供了一个经济实惠的选择，特别是对于那些不需要 70mm 长焦端，但希望保持良好画质和轻巧设计的摄影师来说，Sony FE 24-50mm F2.8 G 绝对是高性价比的选择。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225110" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09244-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09244-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09244.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/21/sony-fe-24-50mm-f2-8-g/dc/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【现场评测】Sony FE 24-50mm F2.8 G 现埸实试　新焦段+轻巧+画质媲美第一代 G Master</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/18/sony-fe-24-50mm-f2-8-g-review/dc/">【评测】Sony FE 24-50mm F2.8 G 轻巧天涯镜，人像实试 + 微距出色</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
